美國政治社會學家[[巴林顿·摩尔|巴林顿·摩尔]]於其《民主和专制的社会起源》一書中提出了以暴力的歷史觀察來介定現代社會走向[[獨裁政體|獨裁政體]]或[[民主政體|民主政體]]，归纳出西方[[议会民主制|议会民主制]]、[[法西斯主义|法西斯主义]]、[[共产主义|共产主义]]和[[伊斯蘭主義|伊斯蘭主義]]四条不同的道路，產生不同現代獨裁者執行國家暴力。<ref name="Moore1987">{{cite book|author=Barrington Moore|title=民主和专制的社会起源|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=0NRtAAAAIAAJ|year=1987|publisher=华夏出版社|access-date=2013-11-20|archive-date=2014-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629200052/http://books.google.com/books?id=0NRtAAAAIAAJ|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Moore2003">{{cite book|author=Barrington Moore|title=Social Origins of Dictatorship and Democracy: Lord and Peasant in the Making of the Modern World|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Ip9W0yWtVO0C|date=2003-09-06|publisher=Beacon Press|isbn=978-0-8070-5073-6|access-date=2013-11-20|archive-date=2014-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140629200123/http://books.google.com/books?id=Ip9W0yWtVO0C|dead-url=no}}</ref>

